    </section>
    <section class="life-work">
        <h2>Life and Work</h2>
        <p>Pawan Kalyan started his career as an actor in Telugu cinema and soon became a popular figure. His films, characterized by strong social messages, resonated with audiences across the region. In 2014, he established the JanaSena Party, aiming to address the issues faced by the common man. His leadership and advocacy for various social causes have made a significant impact on society.</p>
    </section>
    <section class="achievements">
        <h2>Achievements</h2>
