            <li>Founded the JanaSena Party in 2014</li>
            <li>Starred in several blockbuster films</li>
            <li>Known for his philanthropic efforts and social initiatives</li>
            <li>Advocate for farmers' rights and anti-corruption measures</li>
        </ul>
